    "display_name": "Make a Quiz",
    "long_instructions": "## Make a Quiz\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:**\r\n\r\nAsk AI to make a quiz on a topic like a school subject, pop culture, or anything you're curious about.\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nAsk for multiple-choice vs. true/false questions, or try making it \"easy\" or \"challenging.\"\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nAre the questions clear and fair? Do the answers make sense?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n",
